--- !u!114 &1382415744
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1382415742}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.TextMeshPro::TMPro.TextMeshProUGUI
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Can\u0131m o\u011Flum,\r\n\r\nE\u011Fer bu sat\u0131rlar\u0131 okuyorsan,
    bu evin kap\u0131lar\u0131 \xFCzerine \xE7oktan kilitlenmi\u015F ve g\xF6lgeler
    senin i\xE7in k\u0131p\u0131rdamaya ba\u015Flam\u0131\u015F demektir. Seni bu
    sessiz cehenneme, benim g\xFCnahlar\u0131m\u0131n miras\u0131na geri \xE7a\u011F\u0131rd\u0131\u011F\u0131m
    i\xE7in beni asla affetme. Y\u0131llar \xF6nce seni ve aileni korumak ad\u0131na
    karanl\u0131k bir anla\u015Fma yapt\u0131m; bir l\xFCtuf kar\u015F\u0131l\u0131\u011F\u0131nda
    bir ruh verdim. O varl\u0131k, borcun bedeli olarak beni bu duvarlar\u0131n so\u011Fuklu\u011Funa
    hapsetti ama as\u0131l korkum kendim i\xE7in de\u011Fil, senin i\xE7in. \xC7\xFCnk\xFC
    bu ev art\u0131k sadece beni tutsak etmiyor, senin kan\u0131n\u0131 da kendine
    \xE7a\u011F\u0131r\u0131yor. \u015Eafak s\xF6kene kadar buradan \xE7\u0131kamazsan,
    sen de bu ebedi azab\u0131n bir par\xE7as\u0131 olacaks\u0131n.\r\n\r\nBu y\xFCzden
    zaman\u0131m\u0131z dar evlat, \u015Fafak vaktine kadar laneti k\u0131rmal\u0131s\u0131n.
    Yarat\u0131k \u015Fu an seninle beraber ve onun bu evden d\u0131\u015Far\u0131
    \xE7\u0131kmamas\u0131 gerek; bu y\xFCzden evin belirli k\xF6\u015Felerine, e\u015Fiklerine
    kutsal tuzlar\u0131 serpmelisin. Tuz hatt\u0131n\u0131 tamamlay\u0131p evi m\xFCh\xFCrledi\u011Finde,
    art\u0131k bu lanetin ba\u011Flar\u0131n\u0131 koparmaya haz\u0131rs\u0131n demektir.
    Evin d\xF6rt bir yan\u0131na gizlenmi\u015F olan o u\u011Fursuz e\u015Fyalar\u0131
    tek tek bulup yok etmelisin. Onlar yok oldu\u011Funda zincirler gev\u015Feyecek.
    Sonras\u0131nda lanetin ba\u015Flad\u0131\u011F\u0131 yere, yani banyoya gidip
    rit\xFCel duan\u0131 ederek bu kabusu tamamlamal\u0131s\u0131n evlat. Umar\u0131m
    ba\u015Far\u0131rs\u0131n ve bu evin karanl\u0131\u011F\u0131 seni de yutmaz.\r\n\r\nSeni
    \xE7ok seven baban..."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
